comments: Wade (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in Schroder's (BOS) view and gives Schroder a step to avoid the contact.
Horford (BOS) brings his forearm toward Garland's (CLE) front and marginal contact occurs as Garland is passing at the end of the drive.
Valentine's (CLE) left foot is out of bounds when he receives the pass.
Horford (BOS) turns to begin rolling toward the lane as the pick expires and incidental contact occurs with Rubio (CLE) as Rubio goes under.
Horford (BOS) is already in Rubio's (CLE) path when contact occurs and he releases away from the contact.
Valentine (CLE) brushes Horford's (BOS) right arm after he receives the pass and marginal contact occurs prior to Horford's upward shooting motion.
Schroder (BOS) and Wade (CLE) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Rubio (CLE) brushes Schroder's (BOS) right arm as the picks approach and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Wade (CLE) turns alongside Schroder's (BOS) path and marginal body contact occurs after Schroder's gather.
Schroder (BOS) brings his right hand to Wade's (CLE) right arm and initiates contact that restricts Wade's ability to contest the driving shot attempt.
Smart (BOS) moves toward Garland (CLE) and marginal body contact occurs after Garland releases the pass.
Valentine (CLE) and Richardson (BOS) come together at the same spot during rebounding and incidental body contact occurs as Richardson secures the ball.
Schroder (BOS) brings his off-arm toward Wade's (CLE) side and marginal contact occurs as Schroder releases to spin away.
Smart (BOS) and Osman (CLE) come together at the same spot as they position themselves for a potential rebound.
Richardson (BOS) and Valentine (CLE) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Rubio (CLE) does not inbound the ball within five seconds.
Wade (CLE) firms up in his screening position in Schroder's (BOS) path and absorbs the contact.
Garland (CLE) and Schroder (BOS) make incidental arm contact with one another as they each attempt to retrieve the rebound.
Garland (CLE) brings his hands toward Tatum's (BOS) front and Tatum is able to move through the marginal contact to continue dribbling in transition.
Garland (CLE) commits a take foul on Tatum (BOS).
Rubio (CLE) commits a take foul on Schroder (BOS).
Osman (CLE) dribbles toward RIchardson (BOS) in transition and marginal contact occurs as Osman stops short.
Richardson (BOS) cleanly blocks Osman's (CLE) jump shot attempt.
